<div class="row mb-3 mt-3">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mr-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
        <h1 class="text-center">Welcome to Thrift-E!</h1>
        <p class="text-center">
            Thrift-E,
            the startup online clothing Store
            that aims to provide affordable
            clothing options. We are committed to providing stylish, sustainable fashion to everyone. Thrift clothes are secondhand
            or vintage clothing that is
            imported from other countries
            and sold at significantly lower
            prices.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mr-5">
        <img src="/Images/AboutUs/1.jpg" class="w-100">
    </div>
</div>
<hr class="ms-5 me-5">
<div class="row mb-3 mt-3">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 ">
        <img src="/Images/AboutUs/2.jpg" class="w-100">
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
        <h2>Our Unique Value Proposition</h2>
        <p>Thrift-E stands out from other online thrift stores in several ways:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>We offer two categories of clothing: defective clothes and non-defective clothes. This allows our customers to choose the level of quality they want while still being able to shop within their budget.</li>
            <li>We sell clothes at affordable prices, making it easier for our customers to access fashion </li>
            <li>We offer a convenient delivery service that allows you to shop from the comfort of your own home.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
<hr class="ms-5 me-5">
<div class="row mb-3 mt-3">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 mr-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
        <h2 class="text-center">Our Mission and Values</h2>
        <p class="text-center"> Our mission at Thrift-E is to provide affordable, high-quality secondhand clothing and accessories while promoting sustainability. Our core values are accessibility, affordability, reliability, and sustainability for everyone.</p>
